<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Den Design Jewels — Handmade Jewels</title>
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@300;400;600&family=Raleway:wght@300;400;500&display=swap');

    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    :root {
      --greige: #c8bdb0;
      --greige-light: #f0ebe5;
      --greige-dark: #8a7d72;
      --lilla: #9b8bb4;
      --white: #ffffff;
      --text: #4a4440;
      --text-light: #8a7d72;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
      background: var(--white);
      color: var(--text);
    }

    /* NAV */
    nav {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 1.5rem 4rem;
      background: var(--white);
      border-bottom: 1px solid #ece7e2;
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 100;
    }

    .logo-wrap {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.8rem;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .logo-circle {
      width: 48px;
      height: 48px;
      background: var(--greige);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .logo-den {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--white);
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .logo-dot {
      width: 5px;
      height: 5px;
      background: var(--lilla);
      border-radius: 50%;
      margin: 1px auto;
    }

    .logo-design {
      font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.45rem;
      color: var(--white);
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      text-transform: lowercase;
    }

    .logo-text {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: var(--text);
      font-weight: 400;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    }

    nav ul {
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }

    nav a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: var(--text-light);
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }

    nav a:hover { color: var(--lilla); }

    /* HERO */
    .hero {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      min-height: 60vh;
    }

    .hero-left {
      background: var(--greige-light);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 5rem;
    }

    .hero-tag {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.25em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--lilla);
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .hero-left h1 {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 3.5rem;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.2;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .hero-left p {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--text-light);
      line-height: 1.9;
      max-width: 380px;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.8rem 2rem;
      border: 1px solid var(--greige-dark);
      color: var(--text);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      transition: all 0.2s;
      align-self: flex-start;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      background: var(--greige-dark);
      color: var(--white);
    }

    .hero-right {
      background: var(--greige);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero-right img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
	  max-width: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      opacity: 0.9;
    }

    .hero-placeholder {
      text-align: center;
      color: var(--white);
    }

    .hero-placeholder span {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      opacity: 0.7;
    }

    /* SEZIONI */
    .section-title {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 4rem 2rem 2rem;
    }

    .section-title h2 {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--text);
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .section-title p {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--text-light);
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .divider {
      width: 40px;
      height: 1px;
      background: var(--lilla);
      margin: 1rem auto;
    }

    /* GRID COLLEZIONI */
    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 1px;
      background: #ece7e2;
      margin: 0 4rem 4rem;
    }

    .grid-item {
      background: var(--white);
      padding: 2rem;
      text-align: center;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: inherit;
      transition: background 0.2s;
    }

    .grid-item:hover { background: var(--greige-light); }

    .grid-item-icon {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      display: block;
    }

    .grid-item h3 {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .grid-item p {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--text-light);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* BAND */
    .band {
      background: var(--greige-light);
      padding: 4rem;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 4rem;
    }

    .band h2 {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .band p {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: var(--text-light);
      max-width: 400px;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    /* FOOTER */
    footer {
      background: var(--greige);
      padding: 3rem 4rem;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .footer-logo {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: var(--white);
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    }

    .footer-text {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    }

    .footer-lilla {
      width: 8px;
      height: 8px;
      background: var(--lilla);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 0 0.5rem;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <nav>
    <a href="/" class="logo-wrap">
      <div class="logo-circle">
        <span class="logo-den">DEN</span>
        <div class="logo-dot"></div>
        <span class="logo-design">design</span>
      </div>
      <span class="logo-text">Handmade Jewels</span>
    </a>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
      <li><a href="/collezioni">Collezioni</a></li>
      <li><a href="/galleria">Galleria</a></li>
      <li><a href="/chi-sono">Chi sono</a></li>
      <li><a href="/contatti">Contatti</a></li>
    </ul>
  </nav>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-left">
      <div class="hero-tag">Handmade · Artigianale · Unico</div>
      <h1>Gioielli<br/>fatti a mano<br/>con cura</h1>
      <p>Ogni pezzo è unico, creato con materiali selezionati e una cura artigianale che si vede e si sente.</p>
      <a href="/collezioni" class="btn">Scopri le collezioni</a>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-right">
      <img src="/foto-home/foto-home.jpg" alt="Den Design Jewels" />
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="section-title">
    <h2>Le collezioni</h2>
    <div class="divider"></div>
    <p>Pezzi unici fatti a mano</p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid">
    <a href="/collezioni" class="grid-item">
      <span class="grid-item-icon">○</span>
      <h3>Collane</h3>
      <p>Pezzi unici in argento e pietre naturali</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/collezioni" class="grid-item">
      <span class="grid-item-icon">◇</span>
      <h3>Bracciali</h3>
      <p>Eleganza artigianale al polso</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/collezioni" class="grid-item">
      <span class="grid-item-icon">△</span>
      <h3>Orecchini</h3>
      <p>Forme geometriche e materiali naturali</p>
    </a>
  </div>

  <div class="band">
    <h2>Ogni pezzo<br/>racconta una storia</h2>
    <p>I gioielli Den Design nascono da una passione per i materiali, le forme e l'artigianato. Nessun pezzo è uguale all'altro.</p>
    <a href="/chi-sono" class="btn">Scopri di più</a>
  </div>

  <footer>
    <div>
      <div class="footer-logo">Den Design</div>
      <div class="footer-text">Handmade Jewels</div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-text">
      <span class="footer-lilla"></span>
      Fatto con cura · Svizzera
    </div>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>